    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/2635b9de95136afe21ef58faad7468a2.poster.avif?t=1729483513\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/2635b9de95136afe21ef58faad7468a2.webm?t=1729483513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/2635b9de95136afe21ef58faad7468a2.mp4?t=1729483513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>&quot;战到酣处时，耳边刚好响起副歌，玩家的兴奋度就会瞬间攀升到顶峰&quot;9/10 – IGN Japan</strong><br><strong>&quot;Stand-out adventure title and a must-play for VR owners.&quot;(一款惊艳的冒险游戏，VR用户的必玩之作)9/10 – Noisy Pixel</strong><br><br><strong>「眼前的景象并非梦境──」</strong><br>游戏中的将层层改变故事的结局。堪称VR游戏史上篇幅最大的多结局故事。<br>在260年后的未来世界中。你将成为主角克罗依，攻略以探索和对话为主的“冒险模块”，以及操纵人型战斗机器人“巨神机甲”对峙超巨型生物“殒星兽”的“人机互动模块”。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POINT </h2>在“人机互动模块”中，你在战斗时所进行的操作将对故事的后续发展造成影响。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/e3d31101491ef9281912cf9f6f79c193.poster.avif?t=1729483513\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/e3d31101491ef9281912cf9f6f79c193.webm?t=1729483513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/e3d31101491ef9281912cf9f6f79c193.mp4?t=1729483513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在“VR演出模块”中，你将在260年后的世界中，体验光彩夺目的演唱会。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/3f0fd07e64e9b4c29f07f3e46555e03c.poster.avif?t=1729483513\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/3f0fd07e64e9b4c29f07f3e46555e03c.webm?t=1729483513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/3f0fd07e64e9b4c29f07f3e46555e03c.mp4?t=1729483513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在“冒险模块”中，你将在AI给出的备选项中做出选择，推动剧情。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/142efd74e62b03f4ab0c871e029fc327.poster.avif?t=1729483513\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/142efd74e62b03f4ab0c871e029fc327.webm?t=1729483513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/142efd74e62b03f4ab0c871e029fc327.mp4?t=1729483513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在“探索模块”中，你将在VR空间内拿取物品，解开谜底。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/afc60eaef6923e0de341ef122cb7fded.poster.avif?t=1729483513\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/afc60eaef6923e0de341ef122cb7fded.webm?t=1729483513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/afc60eaef6923e0de341ef122cb7fded.mp4?t=1729483513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情梗概</h2>故事发生在2280年。地下都市“A.T(Augmented Tokyo)”凭借以AR技术为中心的科学技术完成了复兴。而这里正是人类最后的堡垒。<br>为了消灭对人类造成毁灭性打击的超巨型生物“殒星兽”，克罗依与战友们坚持不懈地战斗着。其目的只有一个，就是为好友“洸子”报仇。沉重的“决择与选择”接踵而至。你究竟还能扣动扳机吗──？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >适合以下人群 </h2>・想找一部能玩很久的VR大作的玩家<br>・喜欢剧情类游戏、动画和电影的玩家<br>・不擅长高难度操作，但喜欢玩游戏的玩家<br>・想找一部不会头晕的VR游戏的玩家<br>・想实现儿时梦想，燃烧热血的玩家<br>・想亲手操纵机甲的玩家<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502080/extras/4bc1b28b428ddb772480869e79348165.avif?t=1729483513\" width=640 height=360 /></span>",
